King Edward IV
1442-1483
Quarterly, 1st and 4th, France moderne, 2nd and 3rd England[23]
Son of: Richard of York, Duke of York and Cecily Neville.
Declared king in 1461, usurping the crown from the weak King Henry VI.
First king of the House of York.








Elizabeth Woodville
1437-1492
